thread.title_full: Redspot Car Rentals reviewed by K S

author: K S
title: K S
text: I ordered a mid size vehicle according to the website mine could fit 4 adults and 2 suitcases - I got a tiny kia that could barely fit one suitcase there was no parking when I went to return the car as well and some security guy telling you you cant park anywhere else including unmarked available parks just opposite I drove around a few times be fore parking in front of some other redspot vehicles as I was going to be late for my flight
